rows.label: fev11_190_150_msg0003
rows.name:
Are you sure? If you're trying to put
on a brave face, then-

rows.label: fev11_190_150_msg0005
rows.name:
Hey, guys... Do you think we could go
back to the village again?

rows.label: fev11_190_150_msg0008
rows.name:
I was just thinking maybe we could
bring back something to offer to the
rest of the graves, besides Mother's.

rows.label: fev11_190_150_msg0009
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]They were all burned to ashes...
Is there really any point?

rows.label: fev11_190_150_msg0010
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ]Really? We didn't find anything last
time...

rows.label: fev11_190_150_msg0012
rows.name: All right. We can all look together.

rows.label: fev11_190_150_msg0013
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ]If it helps give you closure...
